Package com.sun.identity.password.plugins

Provides interfaces for writing custom plugins for Password Reset Notification and Random Password Generator.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
NotifyPassword NotifyPassword defines a set of methods that are required to notify a user when a password is changed.
PasswordGenerator PasswordGenerator defines a set of methods that are required to generate a new password for a user.
 

Package com.sun.identity.password.plugins Description

Provides interfaces for writing custom plugins for Password Reset Notification and Random Password Generator.
